# Code Owners for github-stars repository
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# IMPORTANT: This file defines code ownership for routing purposes only.
# Branch protection rules must be configured separately in GitHub Settings.
# Do NOT rely on "Require review from Code Owners" without explicit branch rules.

# Global ownership (default)
# Replace @REPLACE_ME_OWNER with actual GitHub username or team
*       @REPLACE_ME_OWNER

# GitHub Actions workflows and configuration
.github/*       @REPLACE_ME_OWNER

# Scripts (especially security-sensitive shell scripts)
scripts/*       @REPLACE_ME_OWNER

# Security policy
SECURITY.md     @REPLACE_ME_SECURITY

# Schema and core data files
schemas/*       @REPLACE_ME_OWNER
repos.yml       @REPLACE_ME_OWNER

# Documentation
docs/*          @REPLACE_ME_OWNER
*.md            @REPLACE_ME_OWNER
